<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent"><b>adzukulu</b> <i>grave diggers</i><br/><br/><b>Charo</b> <i>the ruler of all the land</i><br/><br/><b>chikhwapu</b> <i>giant deadly whip</i><br/><br/><b>chikuse</b> <i>agricultural; heaps of dried maize stalks</i><br/><br/><b>chimanga</b> <i>maize, white</i><a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent"><b>adzukulu</b> <i>grave diggers</i><br /><br /><b>Charo</b> <i>the ruler of all the land</i><br /><br /><b>chikhwapu</b> <i>giant deadly whip</i><br /><br /><b>chikuse</b> <i>agricultural; heaps of dried maize stalks</i><br /><br /><b>chimanga</b> <i>maize, white corn crop</i><br /><br /><b>dambo</b> <i>grassy marsh</i><br /><br /><b>gaga</b> <i>maize chaff</i><br /><br /><b>ganyu</b> <i>handouts</i><br /><br /><b>kape</b> <i>drooling idiot</i><br /><br /><b>magetsi a mphepo</b> <i>windmill, literally "electric wind"</i><br /><br /><b>manglomera</b> <i>magic of superhuman strength</i><br /><br /><b>misala</b> <i>crazy</i><br /><br /><b>mpango</b> <i>long, brightly coloured scarf</i><br /><br /><b>mphala</b> <i>home for unmarried boys</i><br /><br /><b>nkhuli</b> <i>great hunger for meat</i><br /><br /><b>"Odi, odi."</b> <i>"Hello, can I come in?"</i><br /><br /><b>phala</b> <i>maize porridge</i><br /><br /><b>ulimbo</b> <i>sticky sap used as glue, best coming from the nkhaze tree</i><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
