<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/898260-is-there-a-difference-between-this-and-the">Is there a difference between this and the young readers edition? The library gave me the young readers edition, which I don&#39;t mind, but if there is a version not condensed or altered from the original I would prefer to read that one first. Please let me know!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_898260'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6419887-the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind">like</a></span>

</li>
