          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780007316199" href="/book/show/6929749-the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32383826-kristy-k?shelf=1st-person-pov">1st-person-pov</a>, 
