        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1858448483" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13538455389010227691">Incredibly inspirational. William is a boy in Malawi who lives with no electricity, little schooling, and oftentimes hunger. Yet he inspires to do and be more than his situation normally allows. Teaching himself physics and other sciences through books all the while enduring ridicule, he creates a windmill to bring electricity to his home. I was awed and humbled many times throughout his story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


